’espace public.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 7aPHILOSOPHY / General.2bisacsh1 aHaeck, Nicolas, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aPlante, Maxime, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2021z978311127221408iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2021z978311127464540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9782763754079?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782763754079423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782763754079/original  a978-3-11-127221-4  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2021b2021  a978-3-11-127464-5  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2021b2021  aGBV-deGruyter-alles